Definition: a word that expresses a meaning opposed to the meaning of another word, in which case the two words are antonyms of each other
Example: to him the antonym of `gay' was `depressed'
Synonyms: synonym, adj, all, antonymous, opposite_word, opposite, word, a, that, expresses, meaning, opposed, to, the, of, another, in, which, case, two, words, are, antonyms, each, other, him, gay, was, depressed
Category: noun.communication
